15047 /* For a painless codes migration between the STM32F3xx device product */
15048 /* lines, the aliases defined below are put in place to overcome the */
15049 /* differences in the interrupt handlers and IRQn definitions. */
15050 /* No need to update developed interrupt code when moving across */
15051 /* product lines within the same STM32F3 Family */
15052 /******************************************************************************/
